{"id":303312,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/07/维权网-北京公安造假案：被刑拘30天后改写行政拘/","date":"2013-07-12T08:04:39Z","modified":"2013-07-12T08:04:39Z","title":"维权网 | 北京公安造假案：被刑拘30天后改写行政拘留10天（图）","content":"<div dir=\"ltr\">\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员唐韵报道）今年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月以来，北京公安大肆抓捕在京的各地维权访民代表，仅不完全统计就有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>余人因此被刑事拘留。然而，当很多人在被刑事拘留羁押</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">37</span><span>天获释时，或警方不出具任何手续，或出具行政拘留书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>今年的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>，数十名维权访民前去美国大使馆向受台风袭击受灾的美国人献爱心。这一善举被北京公安朝阳分局视为“寻衅滋事”并以此罪名将数十人刑事拘留，并于</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>批捕了天津的许乃来和湖北的何斌。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>就在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日</span><span>这一天，被羁押在朝阳看守所的徐彩虹、何观娇、王次妞、张喜春、林宝钗、刘彦霞、马秀英、李花仙、王继卫、郑全玉等十人，按照办案警察的要求办理了释放手续。而后大家才发现警方出具的不是释放证，是行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>天的处罚决定书。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>徐彩虹说：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">“</span><span>这</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>天我们被关押在北京的看守所，光天化日之下就这么造假，真是骗你没商量！今天我们领略了中国特色的执法</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>。同时我们提醒其他将被刑拘的人，看好了再签字，千万别相信警察，别走我们的路！我们将控诉着一恶意执法行为！</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bJPXxgxz2NQ/Ud-R88xTUNI/AAAAAAAAlJk/ndDkLnIxobs/s1600/2013-07-11+17.35.13.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-bJPXxgxz2NQ/Ud-R88xTUNI/AAAAAAAAlJk/ndDkLnIxobs/s320/2013-07-11+17.35.13.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-MBygnEkBoFU/Ud-R9wP8h2I/AAAAAAAAlJs/_whmzMUeqyo/s1600/2013-07-11+17.35.57.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-MBygnEkBoFU/Ud-R9wP8h2I/AAAAAAAAlJs/_whmzMUeqyo/s320/2013-07-11+17.35.57.jpg\" width=\"240\" /></a></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}